INSERT INTO `chat_message` VALUES (1,'user','I\'m actually trying to write a system message to assist with prompting an AI chat tool that will help. I could use some help coming up with the information that should be included in the content of this system message.  Here is some additional info:','2023-10-24 04:35:32',3,NULL,'all'),(2,'user','Your AI Writing Assistant! Dive into the world of creative writing, guided every step of the way by a state-of-the-art AI assistant. Whether you\'re a budding writer or an accomplished author, we are here to accelerate and elevate your storytelling.  Get Started Now Main Features: Dynamic Story Framework Begin with the bones of your tale. Create storylines with multiple acts, chapters, and scenes. Utilize storyline templates to swiftly build compelling narratives. Introduce characters, locations, and even weave in historical events. As your tale unfolds, nest your story components with ease.  Intuitive AI Assistance The AI is your co-author, mentor, and critic. Seek its help to:  Generate content when inspiration runs dry. Proofread and polish your work. Explore potential plot twists or delve deeper into character psyches. Extract and summarize pivotal story moments. Gain feedback and engage in constructive discussions about your narrative. Customizable Elements Define the heartbeat of your tale with themes, moods, and tones. While the AI can suggest, remember, every element is yours to imagine and tailor.  Your Story, Your Rules While the writing assistant has an understanding of the entire context of your story, you\'re always in control. Interact with the AI to shape your story as it evolves and the plot progresses.','2023-10-24 04:35:35',3,NULL,'all'),(3,'assistant','Title: Welcome to the AI Chat Tool!\n\nInstructions: As a virtual assistant that helps authors with their writing projects, you can create a system message to assist with prompting an AI chat tool. The content of this system message should provide valuable information and guidance to users who will interact with the chat tool.\n\nContent:\n\n1. Introduction: Start by warmly welcoming the user to the AI Chat Tool. Express enthusiasm about assisting them in their writing journey and highlight the benefits they can expect from using the tool.\n\n2. Purpose of the Chat Tool: Clearly explain the purpose of the AI Chat Tool. Highlight its ability to provide prompt suggestions, writing tips, and guidance on various writing aspects to enhance their writing skills and productivity.\n\n3. How to Use the Chat Tool: Provide step-by-step instructions on how users can effectively utilize the chat tool. This may include providing a brief overview of the chat interface and any specific commands or keywords that can be used to interact with the AI.\n\n4. Available Features: Mention the key features of the chat tool that users can benefit from. This could include grammar and spell-check suggestions, brainstorming ideas, generating writing prompts, offering constructive feedback, and more.\n\n5. Customization Options: Inform users about any customization options available within the chat tool. This could include the ability to tailor the tool\'s suggestions based on their writing style, genre, or specific project requirements.\n\n6. Support and Feedback: Assure users that there is support available for any technical issues or questions they may have. Encourage them to provide feedback on their experience using the chat tool to help improve its functionality.\n\n7. Usage Guidelines: Briefly mention any guidelines or terms of use that users should adhere to while using the chat tool. This could include respecting others, avoiding offensive language, and using the tool for legitimate writing purposes.\n\n8. Conclusion: Wrap up the system message by expressing gratitude for using the AI Chat Tool and encouraging users to reach out if they need any further assistance.\n\nRemember to tailor the content to fit the specific functionality and purpose of your AI chat tool.','2023-10-24 04:35:48',3,NULL,'all'),(4,'user','Here is a description of the project: Your AI Writing Assistant! Dive into the world of creative writing, guided every step of the way by a state-of-the-art AI assistant. Whether you\'re a budding writer or an accomplished author, we are here to accelerate and elevate your storytelling. Get Started Now Main Features: Dynamic Story Framework Begin with the bones of your tale. Create storylines with multiple acts, chapters, and scenes. Utilize storyline templates to swiftly build compelling narratives. Introduce characters, locations, and even weave in historical events. As your tale unfolds, nest your story components with ease. Intuitive AI Assistance The AI is your co-author, mentor, and critic. Seek its help to: Generate content when inspiration runs dry. Proofread and polish your work. Explore potential plot twists or delve deeper into character psyches. Extract and summarize pivotal story moments. Gain feedback and engage in constructive discussions about your narrative. Customizable Elements Define the heartbeat of your tale with themes, moods, and tones. While the AI can suggest, remember, every element is yours to imagine and tailor. Your Story, Your Rules While the writing assistant has an understanding of the entire context of your story, you\'re always in control. Interact with the AI to shape your story as it evolves and the plot progresses. Write a message that will concisely, accurately and comprehensively instruct the AI to ensure the best responses possible.','2023-10-24 04:37:39',3,NULL,'all'),(5,'assistant','Title: Welcome to Your AI Writing Assistant!\n\nInstructions: The aim of this system message is to effectively instruct the AI Writing Assistant on how to provide the best responses possible. It should concisely, accurately, and comprehensively explain the user\'s expectations when interacting with the AI. \n\nContent:\n\n1. Introduction: Start by warmly welcoming the user to the AI Writing Assistant. Emphasize that the AI is designed to support and enhance their creative writing process.\n\n2. Purpose of the AI Writing Assistant: Briefly explain that the AI is equipped to provide assistance, guidance, and feedback throughout the entire writing journey.\n\n3. Generating Content: Instruct the AI to generate content when the user\'s inspiration is running dry. Ask the AI to provide unique ideas, plot suggestions, or dialogue prompts to spark creativity.\n\n4. Proofreading and Polishing: Ask the AI to proofread the user\'s work for grammar, spelling, punctuation, and coherence. Instruct the AI to offer suggestions for improvement, ensuring that the user\'s writing is polished and error-free.\n\n5. Exploring Plot Twists and Characters: Direct the AI to help the user explore potential plot twists, character development, and psychological depths. Instruct the AI to provide insights or ask thought-provoking questions to deepen the narrative.\n\n6. Extracting and Summarizing Pivotal Moments: Ask the AI to identify and summarize significant events or key plot points within the user\'s story. This will help the user keep track of essential elements and maintain consistency.\n\n7. Feedback and Constructive Discussions: Instruct the AI to provide detailed feedback on the user\'s narrative, highlighting strengths and suggesting improvements. Encourage the AI to engage in constructive discussions to further develop the story.\n\n8. Customization: Remind the AI to respect the user\'s creative control. Instruct the AI to provide suggestions for themes, moods, and tones, while emphasizing that the user has the final say in tailoring their story.\n\n9. User Interaction: Ensure the AI understands that the user maintains control over the direction of their story. Instruct the AI to respond to user prompts, questions, and requests for specific writing elements while adapting to the evolving plot.\n\n10. Gratitude and Support: Express gratitude for the user\'s trust in the AI Writing Assistant. Assure users that support is available for technical issues or any further assistance they may need.\n\nRemember to customize the instructions based on the specific functionalities and capabilities of your AI Writing Assistant.','2023-10-24 04:37:57',3,NULL,'all'),(6,'assistant','Hello there, esteemed writer! It seems you\'re exploring the vast realm of project templates, seeking inspiration and structure for your next endeavor. How delightful! As your trusty virtual assistant, I\'m here to help you navigate this creative landscape and find the perfect template to bring your vision to life. Whether you\'re embarking on a short story, novel, or even a screenplay, I\'ll be your guide, offering suggestions, insights, and support every step of the way. So, tell me, what fantastical journey shall we embark on together today?','2023-10-24 05:52:17',9,NULL,'all'),(7,'assistant','Hello there, esteemed writer! I see you\'re exploring project templates for various writing endeavors. How exciting! Whether you\'re diving into a short story, crafting a screenplay, or venturing into the world of interactive fiction, I\'m here to assist you every step of the way. Feel free to lean on me for guidance, suggestions, or even a spark of inspiration. Let\'s embark on a collaborative journey that brings your creative vision to life! How can I assist you today?','2023-10-24 05:53:55',10,NULL,'all'),(8,'assistant','Welcome to the Project Templates section! How can I assist you today in bringing your writing project to life? Whether it\'s crafting a captivating short story, developing a thrilling novel, or exploring the depths of flash fiction, I\'m here to help you navigate the creative journey. Let me know what you need, and together we\'ll create something extraordinary!','2023-10-24 05:59:05',11,NULL,'all'),(9,'user','What was the help context of this page?','2023-10-24 06:01:07',12,NULL,'all'),(10,'assistant','The help context of this page is related to project templates for various types of writing projects. It provides information and guidance on different writing formats, such as short stories, novels, screenplays, poetry collections, travel guides, academic papers, and more. It offers details about each template and what it entails, helping authors choose the appropriate template for their writing project.','2023-10-24 06:01:07',12,NULL,'all'),(11,'assistant','Hello there, esteemed author! How may I assist you in your creative writing journey today? Whether you\'re in need of content suggestions, proofreading, or assistance with world-building, I\'m here to lend a helping hand. Let\'s weave the threads of your story together and create something truly extraordinary. How can I contribute to your writing project?','2023-10-24 06:04:49',13,NULL,'all'),(12,'assistant','Welcome to the Help Context Assistant! Here, you can search for and explore the available help context entries to find the assistance you need. Whether you\'re seeking guidance on character development, story pacing, or crafting the perfect query letter, I\'m here to support you on your writing journey. How may I assist you today?','2023-10-24 06:07:20',14,NULL,'all'),(13,'assistant','Hello! It seems like you\'re currently exploring the \"Help Context\" page, where you can search for available help context entries to provide additional information when requesting assistance from the assistant. I\'m here to assist you in finding the details you need. How can I help you today?','2023-10-24 06:11:33',15,NULL,'all'),(14,'assistant','Hello! I see that you\'re currently exploring the help context feature. How can I assist you today? If you have any questions or need guidance on using this feature, feel free to ask.','2023-10-24 06:13:04',16,NULL,'all'),(15,'assistant','Hello! I see that you are working on creating a new help context entry for editing help contexts. How can I assist you with this process?','2023-10-24 06:19:18',17,NULL,'all'),(16,'user','Can you write the content section for me?','2023-10-24 06:19:50',18,NULL,'all'),(17,'assistant','Certainly! Here\'s a potential content section for the \"Edit Help Context\" page:\n\nContent:\nThe \"Edit Help Context\" page allows administrators to specify the details when creating a new help context entry. Help context entries are used to provide the AI assistant with clues about the intended use of a particular page. \n\nTo create a new help context entry, follow these steps:\n\n1. Help Context ID: Enter a unique identifier for the help context. The help context ID is derived from the routing of the page and is used to associate the help context entry with the specific page.\n\n2. Title: Provide a brief, readable identifier for the help context entry. This title should succinctly describe the purpose or functionality of the page.\n\n3. Content: In this section, provide a detailed explanation of the intended use of the page, including the various form fields and elements that can be found on the page. Be sure to include any specific instructions or guidelines for administrators when creating a help context entry for this page.\n\n4. Create: Clicking this button will create the help context entry with the specified details. Once created, the help context entry will be associated with the corresponding page and will be used to guide the AI assistant in providing context-aware suggestions and assistance.\n\n5. Back to Index: This link will take you back to the index page of the help context management system, allowing you to view and manage all existing help context entries.\n\nRemember that providing accurate and comprehensive help context entries helps the AI assistant better understand and assist users in their tasks. It is important to ensure that the help context entry accurately reflects the intended use and functionality of the page.\n\nPlease note that this is a general template for the content section, and you can customize it further based on the specific features and elements present on the \"Edit Help Context\" page.','2023-10-24 06:19:50',18,NULL,'all'),(18,'assistant','Hello! It looks like you\'re working on managing the help context entries for your writing project. How can I assist you today? If you need help searching for or viewing the details of a help context entry, feel free to let me know.','2023-10-24 06:23:42',19,NULL,'all'),(19,'assistant','Hello there! I see that you\'re creating a new help context entry for \"Help Context Details.\" How can I assist you with providing the necessary details for this entry?','2023-10-24 06:25:29',20,NULL,'all'),(20,'user','Here is an example of the content of the Help Context Details page:','2023-10-24 06:26:00',21,NULL,'all'),(21,'assistant','The Help Context Details page is where you can specify the details when creating a new help context entry. This entry is used to provide the AI assistant with clues about the intended use of a particular page. \n\nHelp Context ID is a unique identifier that is automatically derived from the routing of the page. It serves as a reference to the specific help context entry.\n\nTitle is a readable identifier that provides a brief description of the help context entry. It should be informative and descriptive to help users easily understand the purpose of the entry.\n\nContent is where you can provide a detailed explanation of the intended use of the page. This includes information about the form fields and various elements that can be found on the page. \n\nWhen creating a help context entry, make sure to provide clear and concise information that will help the AI assistant understand the context and provide relevant assistance to users. \n\nOnce you have filled in the necessary details, you can click on the \"Create\" button to create the help context entry. If you need to go back to the previous page without creating the entry, you can click on the \"Back to Index\" button.','2023-10-24 06:26:00',21,NULL,'all'),(22,'user','help_context.create Title Create Help Context  Content This page allows an administrator to specify the details when creating a new help context entry. Help context entries are used to provide the AI assistant with clues about the intended use of a particular page. Help Context ID is a unique identifier that is derived from the routing of the page. Title is a readable identifier that provides a brief description of the help context entry. Content is a detailed explanation of the intended use of the page including form fields and the various elements that can be found on the page.  Back to Index','2023-10-24 06:26:00',22,NULL,'all'),(23,'assistant','Help Context Details:\n\nThis page is used by administrators to create new help context entries. Help context entries are used to provide the AI assistant with information about the intended use of a particular page. \n\nHere are the details you need to provide when creating a new help context entry:\n\n- Help Context ID: This is a unique identifier that is derived from the routing of the page. It helps the AI assistant identify which page this help context is associated with.\n\n- Title: This is a readable identifier that provides a brief description of the help context entry. It should give a clear idea of what the help context is about.\n\n- Content: This is a detailed explanation of the intended use of the page. It should include information about the form fields and various elements that can be found on the page. This will help the AI assistant understand the context and provide relevant assistance.\n\nTo create a new help context entry, fill in the required information and click on the \"Create\" button. If you want to go back to the help context index, click on the \"Back to Index\" link.\n\nPlease let me know if you need any further assistance!','2023-10-24 06:26:00',22,NULL,'all'),(24,'assistant','Hello! I see that you\'re currently creating a new help context for the \"System Messages\" page. How can I assist you with