ormation in each system message to effectively communicate with the users.','2023-10-24 06:28:52',24,NULL,'all'),(27,'assistant','Hello! I see that you are currently creating a system message. How can I assist you in crafting a clear and effective message? Whether you need help with the content, tone, or formatting, I\'m here to offer guidance and support. Just let me know what specific assistance you require, and I\'ll be happy to help you!','2023-10-24 06:33:34',25,NULL,'all'),(28,'user','<div id=\"aiw-content\">            <div class=\"container mt-5\">      <h2>Create System Message</h2>       <form action=\"/admin/system_message/create\" method=\"post\" data-dashlane-rid=\"ab894a1914503e18\" data-form-type=\"register\">     <input id=\"csrf_token\" name=\"csrf_token\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"IjkyNGY4M2NiNmVjNjkxZGY5OTkxNDk4MGIyZTY2YjE3MjI0ZTI0Mjgi.ZTdlBg.Xir1rQKoQfkC_IDtw6jp1Oz4F6Q\">      <div class=\"form-group\">       <label for=\"title\">Title</label>       <input class=\"form-control\" id=\"title\" maxlength=\"255\" name=\"title\" required=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\" data-dashlane-rid=\"bfe0076304f10e69\" data-kwimpalastatus=\"alive\" data-kwimpalaid=\"1698129159754-0\" data-dashlane-filled-by-user=\"true\" data-kwcachedvalue=\"System Down\" data-form-type=\"title,job\">     <span id=\"1698129159754-0\" data-dashlanecreated=\"true\" style=\"color: initial; font: initial; font-palette: initial; font-synthesis: initial; forced-color-adjust: initial; text-orientation: initial; text-rendering: initial; -webkit-font-smoothing: initial; -webkit-locale: initial; -webkit-text-orientation: initial; -webkit-writing-mode: initial; writing-mode: initial; zoom: initial; accent-color: initial; place-content: initial; place-items: initial; place-self: initial; alignment-baseline: initial; animation-composition: initial; animation: initial; app-region: initial; appearance: initial; aspect-ratio: initial; backdrop-filter: initial; backface-visibility: initial; backgroun